<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    ANALYSIS: MEDIA CONVERGENCE: IS IT THE NEXT GREAT THING?
 &HT;    Moving in (w) Washington and (f) financial categories for
release Sunday, Jan. 16.
 &HT;    Eds: This article stands for the weekly GLASS-COLUMN.
 &HT;    By ANDREW J. GLASS
 &HT;    c.2000 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   WASHINGTON _ You pick up the phone, and instead of a dial tone
you hear a friendly female voice purr: ``How may I help you?''
