night and Sunday), ``Adieu Poulet'' and ``Peau Neuve.''
</P>
<P>
   TV5 USA, (888) 902-5322; www.tv5.org/usa. The 24-hour satellite
television programming featuring news and films from France,
Belgium, Switzerland, Quebec and French-speaking nations in Africa.
Fees are about $10 a month.
</P>
<P>
   Music
</P>
