</P>
<P>
   Adventure
</P>
<P>
   FRENCH FOREIGN LEGION,
www.info-france-usa.org/america/embassy/legion/legion.htm. The
French Embassy Web site regularly lists cultural events in the
United States, but its most popular page offers information about
enlistment in the French Foreign Legion. (Must be between the age
of 17 and 40, but knowledge of the French language is not
necessary.)
</P>
