14, and runs through Feb. 18. Hours: Mondays through Thursdays, 9
a.m. to 8 p.m.; Fridays, 9 a.m. to 6 p.m.; Saturdays, 9 a.m. to 2
p.m. Free.
</P>
<P>
   Restaurants
</P>
<P>
   LA BONNE SOUPE, 48 W. 55th St., Manhattan, (212) 586-7650.
</P>
<P>
   CHEZ BERNARD, 323 West Broadway, at Broome Street, Soho, (212)
343-2583.
</P>
<P>
   JULES, 65 St. Marks Place, East Village, (212) 477-5560.
</P>
<P>
   CASIMIR, 103-105 Avenue B, between Sixth and Seventh Streets,
East Village, (212) 358-9683.
</P>
