<SLUG> BC-CORRECTIVE-AILING-HMO-BOS </SLUG>
  
 (Eds.: Newspapers that used the Boston Globe story AILING-HMO (a,
f) by Richard A. Knox and Steven Wilmsen, which moved Jan. 12, will
wish to use the following corrective.
<TEXT>
<P>
   &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   Because of a reporting error, a Boston Globe story about
regulators rescinding severance payments for two former executives
at Harvard Pilgrim Health Plan incorrectly stated the total amount
being witheld. The combined total of the severance payments comes
to $1.8 million.
</P>
