of a woman (Bette Midler) whose demise pains absolutely no one in
her small town. (Destination)
</P>
<P>
   East-West: Gullible Russian expatriates take up Stalin's offer
to help rebuild the Soviet Union after World War II. Dumb move.
French film stars Sandrine Bonnaire and Catherine Deneuve. (Sony
Pictures Classics)
</P>
<P>
   My Sweet Killer: A look inside the mind of a disturbed
individual. (FilmKitchen.com)
</P>
<P>
