self-discovery. Directed by Majid Majidi (``The Children of
Heaven''). (Sony Pictures Classics)
</P>
<P>
   East Is East: Pakistani teens living in 1970s London decide to
rebel against their father's traditions. To be honest, we prefer
saris to bellbottoms. (Miramax)
</P>
<P>
   The Ninth Gate: Johnny Depp goes to hell and back in this occult
thriller about a cynical book dealer whose investigation of a
17th-century satanic manual puts him in a devil of a predicament.
Roman Polanski directs. (Artisan)
</P>
<P>
   Romeo Must Die: It's chop socky vs. hip hop as rival Asian and
African-American gangs duke it out on the Oakland waterfront. Stars
Jet Li, Aaliyah and Delroy Lindo. (Warner Bros.)
</P>
