Can you say ``Love Story''? With Leelee Sobieski and Chris Klein.
(Fox)
</P>
<P>
   High Fidelity: John Cusack runs a failing record store (probably
because the guy won't evolve past vinyl) and a love life to match.
Directed by Stephen Frears, who did well with Cusack on ``The
Grifters.'' (Touchstone)
</P>
<P>
   Not Love, Just Frenzy: Three Spanish directors contributed to
this Almodovar-like study of crazy sex and partying in modern
Madrid. (Jour de Fete Films)
</P>
