<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-01-13 19:07 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5376 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u e BC-CAMPAIGN-HILLARY-BOS &LR;      01-13 0653
