Charles Schwab Corp. said Thursday that it will make a leap across
the country and the spectrum of investors to buy U.S. Trust Corp.
for $2.7 billion in stock. By Patrick McGeehan.
</P>
<P>
   (Scheduled to move by 9 p.m. ET.)
