Clinton hugs Barry Gordy, the founder of Motown Records, after
Gordy receives the Millennium Award; Jesse Jackson, right, and
Sanford Weill look on. Clinton proposed giving more tax credits to
businesses that invest in the country's poorest areas. ``It will
