<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-01-13 21:47 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5569 &Cx1f; tad-z
u l BC-GRANDPARENTS14-COX     01-13 0995
