<HEADLINE>
ANTIDRUG CONTENT IN TV SCRIPTS ALLEGEDLY EARNED MILLIONS 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (a and e coding)   (For use by New York Times News Service clients)  
 By MARK JURKOWITZ AND DON AUCOIN  
 c.2000 The Boston Globe  
 
<TEXT>
<P>
   Prime-time television's role as a combatant in the war on drugs
